{"title":"Peach Embellished Anarkali Suit With Dupatta","fabric":"Bead and Thread detailing","model_size":"","info":"","description":"This Peach Embellished Anarkali Suit features heavy embellishment on the neckline. It adds richness. It completes the royal look.
Furthermore, the ankle-length flare drapes beautifully. The fabric flows smoothly. You move freely and confidently. The suit feels light. Yet it appears grand. Therefore, you enjoy comfort and charm together.
A matching dupatta completes this Peach Embellished Anarkali Suit. It comes with delicate borders. The net texture looks sheer and refined. You can drape it in multiple ways. It elevates your outfit effortlessly.
Product Details

Color: Peach
Work: Embellished handwork, bead and thread detailing
Dupatta: Net with embellished border
Length: Ankle-length flare
